别总拿我当小孩嘛

26
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:29,170
Now, take me to return
my Star Wars sheets!
带我去退了那些星战床单啦

27
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:35,030
Penny? Penny? Penny?
Penny? Penny? Penny?

28
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:37,920
