Leonard takes Los Robles Avenue.
Leonard通常走Los Robles大道

67
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,910
Well, good for Leonard.
Leonard真行啊

68
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:05,670
Euclid Avenue is shorter as the
crow flies, but it has speed bumps,
Euclid大道直线距离是短点
可路上有减速带啊

69
00:04:05,700 --> 00:04:10,770
which appreciably increase point-to-point
drive time, making it the less efficient choice.
点对点的行车时间就显著增加
这样一来就不算高效了

70
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:14,150
But you have the conn.
不过方向盘在你手里

71
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,930
Of course, if you're not going
to slow down fothe speed bumps,
当然 如果你通过减速带时不减速

72
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:21,790
I withdraw my previous objection.
我收回我之前的话

73
00:04:23,290 --> 00:04:25,170
Here's a fun question.
问你个有意思的问题

74
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:27,840
Do you know what the most
common street name is?
你知道最常见的街名是啥吗?

75
00:04:27,860 --> 00:04:30,160
- No.
- The answer's tricky.
- 不知道
- 答案很狡猾噢

76
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:32,730
It's Second Street.
是第二大街

77
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:35,360
You see, you'd think it would be
First Street, but in most towns,
大多数人都会认为是第一大街
但在大多数城里

78
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:37,650
First Street eventually gets
renamed to something else.
第一大街最终都会被重新命名

79
00:04:37,670 --> 00:04:41,380
You know, like Main
Street, Broad Street.
比方说美茵街 布罗德街

80
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:43,600
Michigan Avenue.
密歇根大道

81
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:48,560
See, Leonard and I often use our commute time to
exercise our minds with brain-teasers like that.
看没 我和Leonard总用路上时间
玩玩脑筋急转弯锻炼脑子

82
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:51,510
We also play games.
我们还做游戏

83
00:04:52,130 --> 00:04:54,570
- Would you like to play one?
- No.
- 来玩个不?
- 不用了

84
00:04:54,580 --> 00:04:56,980
Oh, come on. It's fun.
噢 来吧 可有意思呢

85
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:59,440
Another bump.
又不减速 弹咯

86
00:05:00,580 --> 00:05:03,990
Okay. I'll say an element,
and, and you say an element
好咧 我来说一个元素名
然后 你再说一个

87
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:07,710
whose name starts with the last
letter of the one I said, okay?
像接龙一样 首尾字母相接 怎么样?

88
00:05:08,740 --> 00:05:10,870
I'll start.
我先开始

89
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,990
Helium.
氦(helium)

90
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:19,070
Now, you could say "mercury."
你可以接"汞"(mercury)

91
00:05:19,090 --> 00:05:22,920
That would give me a "y." Very
clever. That's a tough one.
我就要用"y"开头 真聪明 这有点难度

92
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:26,870
So I go with "ytterbium,"
which gets you back to "m."
那我就接"镱"(ytterbium) 你又得用"m"开头了

93
00:05:26,910 --> 00:05:31,070
So you go "molybdenum,"
and I say "magnesium."
那你就接"钼"(molybdenum)
然后我接"镁"(magnesium)

94
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,680
You say "manganese."
你接"锰"(manganese)

95
00:05:32,710 --> 00:05:36,730
I say "europium," and, then, you're
left with "mendelevium," and...
我接"铕"(europium) 然后你
就只能接"钔"(Mendelevium) 这样一来...

96
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:40,490
there are no more m's because I believe that
meitnerium should still be called ekairidium.
就没有以"m"开头的了
因为我觉得"钔"还是该叫"类铅"(Ekairidium)

97
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:43,180
So, congratulations. You win.
恭喜啊 你赢了

98
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:50,330
Do you wanna go again?
你想再来一遍吗?

99
00:05:50,340 --> 00:05:53,230
Why don't we just have
a little quiet time now?
你就不能消停一会儿吗

100
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:55,510
All right.
好吧

101
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:00,630
I'm sorry.
对不起

102
00:06:00,670 --> 00:06:05,720
I'm finding your reckless nonchalance regarding
the check-engine light to be very troubling.
你对"检查引擎"无所谓的冷漠态度
让我感到极度不安

103
00:06:09,170 --> 00:06:11,250
Get out.
下车

104
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,270
Well, I have to tell you that
好吧 我跟你实话实说

105
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:17,200
while I do have a theoretical understanding of
the workings of an internal combustion engine,
我的确对内燃引擎的工作原理有所了解

106
00:06:17,230 --> 00:06:20,440
I'm not sure I'm capable
of performing diagnostics.
可我不确定我是否能进行故障排查

107
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:22,470
I said, "Get out."
我说"下车"

108
00:06:22,490 --> 00:06:25,290
Okay. I'll give it a shot.
好吧 我来试试好了

109
00:06:38,670 --> 00:06:40,740
Oh, Leonard. There you are.
噢 Leonard 你在这儿啊

110
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:43,200
I'm ready to go home.
我准备回家了

111
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:47,170
- I just got here.
- Good. Perfect timing.
- 我才刚来
- 太好了 时间算得够准的

112
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:51,330
Sheldon, I told you, I only have access
to the free-electron laser at night.
Sheldon 我跟你说过了
我只有晚上才能用自由电子激光仪

113
00:06:51,350 --> 00:06:53,040
I can't drive you for
the next few weeks.
接下来几个礼拜我都不能开车送你了

114
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:55,350
No, you said you
couldn't drive me to work.
不 你只是说你不能开车送我上班

115
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:58,080
This is from work.
现在是下班

116
00:06:58,090 --> 00:06:59,850
Howard, help me out here.
Howard 救救我吧

117
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:03,170
No, just for the fun of
it, I'm gonna take his side.
才不呢 为了乐子 我也要站在他那边

118
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:07,070
Now, how do you propose I get home?
那你觉得我该怎么回家?

119
00:07:07,090 --> 00:07:08,830
How did you get here in the first place?
你是怎么来的?

120
00:07:08,850 --> 00:07:10,160
Penny.
Penny送我来的

121
00:07:10,170 --> 00:07:12,880
But I sense that's no longer an option.
但我感觉再也不可能了

122
00:07:14,070 --> 00:07:15,660
Look, I need to get to the laser lab.
听着 我现在要去激光实验室

123
00:07:15,670 --> 00:07:19,410
You're just gonna have to find
someone else to take you home.
你就找别人送你回去吧

124
00:07:25,340 --> 00:07:28,230
Ah, damn, I picked the wrong side.
噢 可恶 我站错边了

125
00:07:33,550 --> 00:07:37,040
Oh, God, not Euclid Avenue!
噢 天呐 表又走Euclid大道嘛!

126
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:46,620
Why did Howard leave you in
the middle of the road anyway?
Howard为啥在半路上把你抛下?

127
00:07:47,810 --> 00:07:49,620
We had a difference of opinion.
我们意见不合

128
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:51,270
Over what?
什么事?

129
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:53,880
Whether or not he was trying to kill me.
就他是否打算杀了我这件事

130
00:07:53,910 --> 00:07:57,120
For the record, I maintain he was.
提一句哈 我仍认为他要杀我

131
00:07:58,230 --> 00:07:59,190
Where are you going?
你这是要上哪儿?

132
00:07:59,210 --> 00:08:00,310
I'm taking you home.
送你回家啊

133
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:02,610
Oh, but I'm not going
home. It's Wednesday.
噢 可我不要回家 今天是礼拜三

134
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:04,000
Wednesday's new comic book day.
礼拜三是"漫画书淘宝"日

135
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:06,610
We have to go to the comic book store.
我们得去漫画书屋

136
00:08:06,620 --> 00:08:10,540
