143
00:08:57,620 --> 00:09:00,590
Good morning.
早上好

144
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,830
Good morning.
早上好

145
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,960
Sheldon, sit down.
Sheldon 坐下

146
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:07,870
She's in my spot.
她占了我的地方

147
00:09:09,260 --> 00:09:12,240
Don't look at me like that.
Everybody knows that's my spot.
别瞪我 谁都知道那是我的地方

148
00:09:17,350 --> 00:09:21,470
Sheldon, you know
that we care about you.
Sheldon 你知道我们都很关心你

149
00:09:21,490 --> 00:09:25,940
